title: Mindless Self Indulgence Remix Stems
description:
These are the remix stems for the following songs:

Evening Wear
Issues
Lights Out
Mastermind
On It
Pay For It
Prescription

and a bonus Mark David Chapman instrumental, although it cuts off at the end (I will try to get this fixed, if possible).

~
